{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_cui_tong","speaker_name":"崔桐","listener":null,"text":"我叫崔桐。我练的是大洪拳。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"很好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"这次你……","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"这次我说很好的意思，就是说他可以在家里好好休养。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":null,"text":"很好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":21,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":null,"text":"这次我的意思，就是希望他打我一拳。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":23,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":43,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"看来他也可以陪崔桐一起在家休养休养了。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":3,"line_start":45,"line_end":45},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"他们二十七位都可以在家休养休养。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":47,"line_end":47},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你一个人都不带？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"我不想去送死。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":51,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你想带谁去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":53,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"带今天没有来的两个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":55,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"今天没有来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":57,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"今天虽然没有来，昨天晚上却来了，一个还给了我一剑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":59,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你也一给了他们一拳，难道还嫌不够？还要找他们来出气？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":63,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"我本来的确不喜欢这种背地暗算的人，可是要对付狼人，他们这种人正合适。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":67,"line_end":67},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"为什么你选来选去，选中的都是女孩子？","tone":"无奈","chapter":3,"line_start":71,"line_end":71},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"她们是孩子？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":3,"line_start":73,"line_end":73},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"不但是女孩子，而且都香得很。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":75,"line_end":75},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"很好，好极了，这次我的意思，就是真的好极了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":3,"line_start":77,"line_end":77},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"只有一点不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":81,"line_end":81},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"哪一点？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":83,"line_end":83},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"现在她们的脸，都被你打肿了，人虽然还香，看起来都有点象猪八戒。","tone":"调侃","chapter":3,"line_start":85,"line_end":85}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_cui_tong","name":"崔桐","alias":[],"identity":"江湖大汉","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"二十七条大汉之一，练大洪拳","personality":{"traits":["豪爽","